article.headline: Zilinskas scores 32 as IU Indianapolis downs Alabama A&M 88-83
article.description: — Paul Zilinskas put up 32 points as IU Indianapolis beat Alabama A&M 88-83 on Monday.
article.linkText: Zilinskas scores 32 as IU Indianapolis downs Alabama A&M 88-83
article.story: HUNTSVILLE, Ala. -- — Paul Zilinskas put up 32 points as IU Indianapolis beat Alabama A&M 88-83 on Monday. Zilinskas shot 11 for 20 (5 for 10 from 3-point range) and 5 of 5 from the free-throw line for the Jaguars (3-5). Jarvis Walker scored 13 points while going 3 of 9 from the floor, including 2 for 5 from 3-point range, and 5 for 7 from the line. Timaris Brown and Sean Craight both added 11 points. Darius Ford led the Bulldogs (4-4) in scoring, finishing with 20 points, six rebounds, seven assists and two steals. Anthony Bryant added 17 points for Alabama A&M. Chad Moodie also had 16 points and three blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
